</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFFCFFBDFF3D9E23683C7F9F" blockId="17.[151,756,552,766]" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFFCFFBDFF3D9E2368C47F1E" bold="true" box="[151,457,615,639]" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">Stratigraphic distribution:</emphasis>
