<collectingRegion id="8818F811FFFCFFBDFD8F9EC36B777FFE" box="[549,634,647,671]" country="Mexico" name="Mexico" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">Mexico</collectingRegion>
. It is also recorded from the Paleocene of northern 
<collectingRegion id="8818F811FFFCFFBDFDF69EE36B9E7FDE" box="[604,659,679,703]" country="Egypt" name="Shamal Sina'" pageId="17" pageNumber="31">Sinai</collectingRegion>
by SAID &amp; KENAWY (1956). In the study area, it is found in the Maastrichtian.
</paragraph>
